div.div: This is an era that belongs to the warriors. They are the law. Powerful and honorable, they decide life and death. Blood drawn by the swords are the melody of this era. In the midst of all this a lone boy, after the death of his grandfather, sets on journey to find his father who fights in the battlefield.

On their wedding day, he was thrown out by his wife and forced to return to his own home, where he was suddenly ambushed by a glamorous woman searching for a kiss. The moment their lips touched, he felt a torrent of energy surge through his body. When he woke up again, his mind was filled with the memories of thousands of strangers... (Source: Tencent, translated)
